## FASE 1 — MAPEAMENTO E DECOMPOSIÇÃO LÓGICA

### 1. Mapa de Partes Lógicas

| # | Parte | Arquivo Principal | Consome | Produz |
|---|-------|------------------|---------|--------|
| 1 | **View Orquestradora** | [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/app/%5Bcontext%5D/gestao-carregadores/page.tsx) | [useChargerData](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/hooks/useChargerData.ts#32-101), `chargerService`, [ContextGuard](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/components/auth/ContextGuard.tsx#13-67) | Layout + disparo de modais |
| 2 | **Data Hook (SWR)** | [useChargerData.ts](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/hooks/useChargerData.ts) | `chargerService` (fetchKanban, fetchChargers, fetchGlobalSchedule) | `kanbanData`, [chargers](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/routers/chargers.py#322-340), `stats`, `loading`, `refresh` |
| 3 | **HTTP Client Layer** | [chargerService.ts](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/lib/api/chargerService.ts) | [httpClient.ts](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/lib/api/httpClient.ts) (request + API_BASE) | 15 funções tipadas (fetch + mutate) |
| 4 | **API Router Backend** | [chargers.py](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/routers/chargers.py) | Schemas Pydantic, [ChargerService](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/services/charger_service.py#23-280), `charger_commands` | 14 endpoints REST |
| 5 | **Read Queries (DB)** | [charger_service.py](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/services/charger_service.py) + [charger_queries.py](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/services/charger_queries.py) | MySQL GLPI (8 SQLs raw) | [KanbanResponse](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/types/charger.ts#146-150), [RankingResponse](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/schemas/charger_schemas.py#114-118), [TicketDetailResponse](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/types/charger.ts#125-138) |
| 6 | **Write Commands (GLPI API)** | [charger_commands.py](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/app/services/charger_commands.py) | `GLPIClient` (session do usuário logado) | Mutações GLPI (assign, create, delete, offline, schedule) |

### 2. Fluxo de Dados

```mermaid
graph TD
    U[Usuário Autenticado] -->|Rota ContextGuard| P1[page.tsx]
    P1 -->|SWR mount| P2[useChargerData Hook]
    P2 -->|fetch every 15/30s| P3[chargerService.ts]
    P3 -->|HTTP + Session-Token| P4[chargers.py Router]
    P4 -->|SELECT| P5[charger_service.py → MySQL]
    P4 -->|CRUD via API| P6[charger_commands.py → GLPI PHP]
    P5 -->|KanbanResponse JSON| P4
    P4 -->|JSON| P3
    P3 -->|Deserialized| P2
    P2 -->|kanbanData + stats| P1
```

### 3. Dependências Externas

| Dependência | Tipo | Criticidade |
|-------------|------|-------------|
| MySQL GLPI (5 tabelas + 2 plugins) | Banco de Dados | **Alta** |
| API REST GLPI PHP | Integração | **Alta** |
| SWR Cache (polling 15s/30s) | Biblioteca | Média |
| `useAuthStore` (token de sessão) | Estado Global | **Alta** |

### 4. Pontos de Fronteira

- **Entrada Frontend:** Rota `/{context}/gestao-carregadores` → `ContextGuard featureId="chargers"` (2 camadas: `requiredRoles` + `requireApp`)
- **Entrada Backend:** Router com `Depends(verify_session)` → aceita `X-Session-Token`, `Session-Token` ou cookie
- **Saída:** Dados visuais em tempo real + mutações que afetam diretamente o GLPI legado

